<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="az">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Səhifə Tapılmadı</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        .error-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 50px;
            max-width: 600px;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 120px;
            font-weight: 900;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1;
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
            50% {
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }
        }
        
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 80px;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
        }
        
        .error-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .error-description {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .btn-custom {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
        }
        
        .btn-custom:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .btn-outline-custom {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            color: #667eea;
            padding: 13px 38px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px;
        }
        
        .btn-outline-custom:hover {
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <i class="fas fa-search error-icon"></i>
        <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
        <h2 class="error-title">Səhifə Tapılmadı</h2>
        <p class="error-description">
            Axtardığınız səhifə mövcud deyil və ya köçürülüb. Zəhmət olmasa əsas səhifəyə qayıdın və ya aşağıdakı düymələrdən istifadə edin.
        </p>
        <div>
            <a href="/" class="btn-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Ana Səhifə
            </a>
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn-outline-custom">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Geri Qayıt
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.3.2/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>